<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>缺口；间隔；差距；分歧：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>generation gap</strong>
代沟</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>bridge / narrow the gap</strong>
消除/缩小差距</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some students are taking a <strong>gap year</strong> to earn money before going to university.
有些学生在上大学前空出一年时间去挣钱。</p><footer>2015 全国改</footer></div></div>